{"id": "1200811428068737106", "channel_id": "1200811428068737106", "type": 0, "author_id": "1079677800023347250", "author_name": "juzi6912", "author_bot": false, "content": "請問官方可以給一個核心機制放在3啟的理由嗎？大小月卡通時課，新喚醒體理想突破也就是1+1，放到3啟是不是有意在篩選玩家群體？還有，不說限時池3個月復刻，限時池1年之後進常駐池不怕玩家那個時候已經流失大半了嘛？這個遊戲的定位究竟是重養成還是重卡牌玩法？不存在又重視養成又重視卡牌的現象，因為那是原神。", "timestamp": "2024-01-27T14:35:54.449000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1200811428068737106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "喚醒體核心機制3啟是不是在篩選玩家？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1200647409919864913", "channel_id": "1200647409919864913", "type": 0, "author_id": "840883092499464222", "author_name": "starry_1018", "author_bot": false, "content": "如題，希洛在最終戰吞噬後，沒有計入幻夢深潛和關卡成就中的最終戰抽牌任務", "timestamp": "2024-01-27T03:44:09.475000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1200647409919864913", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」希洛的吞噬無法完成抽牌任務", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1186103872205369424"]}
{"id": "1200810568517423204", "channel_id": "1200810568517423204", "type": 0, "author_id": "1179795864890392577", "author_name": "halaleung", "author_bot": false, "content": "这游戏角色120保底，而且很多关键机制都拆到命座里，对想要体验多个阵容的玩家不太友好\n\n游戏前期送的银芯很多很棒，可一但开荒完银芯的获取极其匮乏，一个版本存不了一个角色保底\n\n如果不考虑提升抽取概率，可否增加点流明之芯相关礼包，直充给人的氪金体验挺差的\n\n你们看看后台数据，我估计除了体力礼包，其他礼包根本没几个人买，这样你们也很尴尬啊", "timestamp": "2024-01-27T14:32:29.516000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1200810568764903626", "filename": "IMG_9228.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 901373, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1200810568517423204/1200810568764903626/IMG_9228.png?ex=6a0096fd&is=69ff457d&hm=bd82c0e30c15135f49ca9808f60e82e2b353a65e5621326524108c4b46514f14&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1200810568517423204", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」可否增加流明之芯相关礼包", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1200856771875586048", "channel_id": "1200856771875586048", "type": 0, "author_id": "841362944934543400", "author_name": "2kageyama4", "author_bot": false, "content": "前期急着推进度跳了剧情，现在想重新看但是实在是不想再重新打个关卡了，打牌真的很耗时间......cg做成相册之类的功能也会方便查看截图", "timestamp": "2024-01-27T17:36:05.255000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1200856771875586048", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」希望能出一个剧情模式/cg相册之类的功能，还有能在游戏里查看角色全身立绘的地方.....", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1200747452114939925", "channel_id": "1200747452114939925", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "如图，大致说明了我作为均养玩家最开始的想法和如今的困境，希望官方尽早改善游戏体验。", "timestamp": "2024-01-27T10:21:41.393000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🫨", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1200747452563726356", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 653862, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1200747452114939925/1200747452563726356/image.png?ex=6a005c35&is=69ff0ab5&hm=959cef64d57dadc9821f44b502ed5654fcf4db40fd9e39ad67d5b2dfda349b5e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1200747452114939925", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」均衡养成玩家的起源与窘境", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1181168158678204497", "1181168183319736412"]}
{"id": "1200794375924482120", "channel_id": "1200794375924482120", "type": 0, "author_id": "1157675500014153860", "author_name": "youluo0436", "author_bot": false, "content": "這邊有以下幾個建議希望官方可以考慮並實裝進入遊戲中。\n\n1.）劇情模式\n\n希望會出，不然每一次要重溫劇情都要再打一遍關卡很麻煩……\n\n2.）自選UP\n\n可以考慮實裝進常駐池裡，讓各位守密人自選命輪和角色。\n\n如果選擇該角色或該命輪的話那麼這個角色或命輪的概率就會提高，如果抽到了不是自己選的命輪或角色的話，那麼下一次抽到時就必定是自己選的命輪或角色\n\n3.）角色時裝\n\n希望可以出角色們的其他服裝……，也想看他們穿其他衣服的樣子！（算是我個人的私心……）\n\n也希望多出一點SR角色！", "timestamp": "2024-01-27T13:28:08.901000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1200794375924482120", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」忘卻前夜 遊戲建議", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
